{"tid":748723,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(辦公室)好唔好同新黎女同事講？","createTime":"2018-07-19T12:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T13:00:35.000Z","uid":35739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"161cffbe5d2822688e1dcfbfb924b9ba70c98d88","tid":748723,"uid":35739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"事源我聽日last day，有個新同事黎，咁部門就有三個固定兩個臨時黎幫手(A同事&amp;新同事)加經理，固定既同事，咁就一人一部電腦，因為有電腦先需要落手做都幾忙，冇既就執頭執尾輕鬆。<br />\n<br />\n咁問題就黎，今日A襯新同事唔係度，同經理講叫新同事之後接手我部電腦落手做因為佢唔識做，但我知佢扮野，係佢知忙如果識做後會多左野做，連試都唔試，其實普通人都做得黎。<br />\n<br />\n平時都睇唔過眼A好懶冇乜做野，根本冇減少我地工作量，新同學就今日先慢慢學緊點做，個經理又係柒下柒下個種黎，細既話點就點。<br />\n<br />\n好唔好同新同事講翻呢單野，對佢公平啲又好，等佢自己同經理deal又好，起碼唔洗傻下傻下做左粗重野都唔知，最主要唔想A繼續懶到乜都唔洗做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03fafdd8647190a9ab9574215623d8ffeef5955","tid":748723,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"大波就講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7a481316eda26dfd0fa7a120016173e0a7fcb9","tid":748723,"uid":35739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03fafdd8647190a9ab9574215623d8ffeef5955","tid":748723,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"大波就講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546aab61b67a081817e7c68d8d63f0b200f2a023","tid":748723,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7a481316eda26dfd0fa7a120016173e0a7fcb9","tid":748723,"uid":35739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03fafdd8647190a9ab9574215623d8ffeef5955","tid":748723,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"大波就講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"留低電話<br />\n做得唔開心有後路俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}